	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=255703"><span id=" ">Fuhgly</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">6 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score:</span> Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>3 kinds of clickies.&nbsp;&nbsp;Before the cast time, you will see 1 of the following identifiers:<br/><br/>Must Equip - Means you have to put it on to use clicky.<br/><br/>Can Equip - Only those classes that are on the Race and Class list to wear it can click it, but they don't have to equip it.<br/><br/>[Nothing] -  means anyone can click it from inventory, even if they can't wear it.<br/><br/>HTH</p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br />Fuhgly Mofacker<br/>Nature Gaurd<br/>Saryrn</td></tr>
