	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=4599"><span id=" ">Nosferatu</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">324 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score:</span> Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>It's actually quite easy to find out what it doesn't stack with (which will assist you in knowing what it <b>does</b> stack with).&nbsp;&nbsp;Here's how:<br/><br/>Click on the spell name above (not in the picture).  On this screen, click the link called &quot;Lucy Spell View&quot;.  Now, on this screen, in the upper right corner in yellow, you can see a link called &quot;Stacking&quot;.  Click that.<br/><br/>This will give you a list of what it doesn't stack with. <a href=HTTP://lucy.allakhazam.com/stacking.html?id=3713&amp;source=Live target=akztarg>Here's that page</a>.  As you can see, KEI (and it's line on down to Breeze)...Paragon of Spirit (and all other BST Regen)...Nines...etc. are all <b>NOT</b> on there.  This means that it will stack with those.<br/><br/>This makes this item even more &quot;uber&quot;, IMO.</p>&nbsp;<br /></td></tr>
